@startuml level4_hybrid
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10

title **Level 4 — Hybrid Hierarchical Organization**\n//Sequential pipeline + EM review after each agent (max 1 revision)//

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
start
:Decompose question &\ncreate analysis plan;

|#E8F5E9|Market Researcher\n(qwen3:14b)|
:Receive plan;
:Produce market analysis\n(competitors, trends, segments);

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
:Review market analysis;
if (Quality sufficient?) then (yes)
else (no)
  |#E8F5E9|Market Researcher\n(qwen3:14b)|
  :Revise with EM feedback;
  |#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
  :Accept revised output;
endif

|#FFF3E0|Financial Analyst\n(qwen3:14b)|
:Receive plan + market analysis;
:Produce financial analysis\n(costs, revenue, ROI, break-even);

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
:Review financial analysis;
if (Quality sufficient?) then (yes)
else (no)
  |#FFF3E0|Financial Analyst\n(qwen3:14b)|
  :Revise with EM feedback;
  |#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
  :Accept revised output;
endif

|#FFEBEE|Risk Analyst\n(qwen3:14b)|
:Receive plan + market +\nfinancial analyses;
:Produce risk assessment\n(regulatory, market, operational);

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
:Review risk assessment;
if (Quality sufficient?) then (yes)
else (no)
  |#FFEBEE|Risk Analyst\n(qwen3:14b)|
  :Revise with EM feedback;
  |#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
  :Accept revised output;
endif

|#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant\n(qwen3.5:27b)|
:Receive all analyses;
:Synthesize into final consulting\nreport with options & tradeoffs;

|#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
:Review final report;
if (Quality sufficient?) then (yes)
else (no)
  |#F3E5F5|Strategy Consultant\n(qwen3.5:27b)|
  :Revise with EM feedback;
  |#E3F2FD|Engagement Manager\n(qwen3:8b)|
  :Accept revised report;
endif

|#FFFDE7|Evaluator\n(Claude Opus 4.6 — Anthropic API)|
:Score on 6-criterion rubric;
:Produce evaluation scorecard;
stop

note right
  **Hybrid Hierarchical characteristics:**
  * Sequential pipeline: EM → MR → FA → RA → SC → EV
  * EM reviews output after each specialist
  * Max 1 revision per agent
  * Cumulative data routing (each agent gets all prior outputs)
  * No cross-agent iteration (EM is sole quality gate)
  * Local inference (Ollama) except Evaluator (Anthropic API)
end note

@enduml
